Text: I was having problems connecting to the default tracker tpb.thepiratebay.org/announce. I added the tracker tracker.prq.to/announce and it works!

Unfortunately, the title track by Cobalt 60 has a skip in it... that song is the whole reason I downloaded this torrent. I wish it would be re-encoded. If you ever re-encode or see one again, please send me a message.
